title: The Three Stooges - Overcomplete H264 collection [MULVAcoded]
description:
This overcomplete Three Stooges collection includes all Three Stooges shorts 
in high quality plus a stockload of extras like all colourized shorts, solo 
performances and shorts before they were known as the Three Stooges.

This collection contains all entries (including the specials) 
listed at http://thetvdb.com/?tab=series&id=79173&lid=7 (excludes listed below).

They are all named accordingly for mediacenter software like XBMC/KODI to pick 
them up correctly in their library.

These are mostly high quality video files, ripped from DVD source by me. A 
number of specials however were recoded from different sources. Some are of low 
quality, they are marked (low quality) in the file name.

Listed on The TVDB as special, but missing from this pack are these :

77	Stop! Look! and Laugh!	1960-07-01	<-- Excluded feature
78	Snow White and the Three Stooges	1961-06-21	<-- Excluded feature
79	Three Stooges Meet Hercules	1962-02-15	<-- Excluded feature
80	Three Stooges Meet Hercules Part 2	1962-02-15	<-- Excluded feature
81	Three Stooges in Orbit	1962-07-04	<-- Excluded feature
83	Stooges: The Men Behind the Mayhem	1994-12-23	<-- Missing
84	The Three Stooges Movie	2000-04-24	<-- Excluded feature
85	The Three Stooges (Movie)	2012-08-22	<-- Excluded feature
89	Soup to Nuts	1930-09-28	<-- Missing

The other 13 missing entries are as far as I could see duplicates of shorts,
which are all included in this pack.
